description:
It has been two seasons since we have seen Adrianna
Nicole. Back then she was "Seven". Adrianna is back
and she's serious about wanting to wrestle. She is
big and strong, but she lacks technique.
Devi Lynne (ranked 7th) is Spartica! She's a little 5'1 100 lb
hellcat that is 100% go. This former college wrestler
has great skill but is often out-gunned in size and
weight. Can her experience be enough to overcome the
6 inches and 40lbs that her opponent has over her?
title: Devi Lynne "Spartica" (0-1)
